</i></li><li style=""><i>Super kill messages now display the name of the Super used<br />
</i></li><li style=""><i>Voice channel settings in Nav Mode have been moved into the Nav Mode toggle display, which also includes quests &amp; bounties, active modifiers, and PvP Scoreboard<br />
